personal neovim setup
---

Created following 0 to LSP by ThePrimeagen
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w7i4amO_zaE

dependencies
---
- ripgrep   -> text search in folder "<leader>ps"
- xclip     -> yank to clipboard "<leader>y"

- clangd        -> C lsp
- cmake         -> make lsp
- lua_ls        -> lua lsp
- phpactor      -> php lsp
- rust-analyzer -> rust lsp

